-Features-
-Dwarf Multi-cannon -Target System -Bank Tabs -Switchable gameframes -Client settings -Duo Slayer -Money Pouch -Revenant cave -Trivia Bots -Killsteam system -All skills trainable with their own skilling zone -Player user titles -63 wave jad, log out between waves supported -Curses/quick prayers -Full summoning with working specials -Stable economy -Pking is fun, and worth value -Perfect boss animations with multiple attack styles -Great shops to fulfill the needs of players -Working clue scrolls -Perfect bridding, welfare, pure, range, mage pking -Great pvm community -Unique barrows with interface -Very unique teleport interface (many teleports)
Please Comment and Suggest Ideas!!!
-Interbellum
